Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷不在的时候 处处都要小心谨慎不能疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 火车旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早就想体验一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 菲尼 不要擅自在这里跑来跑去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许碰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是珍贵的学术资料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂不懂这个价值多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃伊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近资产家们中好像掀起了一股收集埃及古董的热潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃伊也是珍贵藏品之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是收藏品?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊 请宽恕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我快点搬进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要轻拿轻放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请主保佑汝等免遭劫难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:37.64,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}たとえ終わる事の無い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:37.64,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tatoe owaru koto no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.41,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kanashimi ga anata ubattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.41,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}悲しみがあなた奪っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}hanarete yuku kokoro nado
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.63,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}離れてゆく心など
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:48.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}koko ni wa nai to itte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:48.52,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}此処には無いと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kakeyotta senaka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.34,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}駆け寄った背中に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:03.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}toikakeru ashita ga donna katachi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:03.54,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}問いかける明日がどんあ形でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}yuruga nakatta no wa mou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.57,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}揺るがなかったのはもう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:11.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}shinjiru koto wo wasuretaku nakatta kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:11.29,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}信じる事を忘れたくなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:19.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}me wo sorasu kuse mo aimai na taido mo waraenu uso mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:19.70,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}目を逸らす癖も 曖昧な回答も 笑えぬ嘘も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:26.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tonari ni inakereba ima sae nijin de yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:26.97,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}隣に居なければ意味さえ 滲んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.67,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}たとえ終わる事の無い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.67,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tatoe owaru koto no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:35.44,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}悲しみがあなた奪っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:35.44,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kanashimi ga anata ubattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:42.80,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}忘れないで「さよなら」が 嘘と思えた日々を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:42.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}wasurenai de "sayonara" ga uso to omoeta hibi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:47.64,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}たとえ終わる事の無い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:47.64,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tatoe owaru koto no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.36,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}悲しみがあなた奪っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kanashimi ga anata ubattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.66,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}離れてゆく心など
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}hanarete yuku kokoro nado
